00:21:13.680 --> 00:21:21.550
make meaningful words. So using some
English examples, sat, sit, sad. Each time

00:21:21.730 --> 00:21:29.260
I change one of the sounds we get a
different word. Sat, bat, fat, same thing.

00:21:29.440 --> 00:21:37.480
So what I'm going to argue for is that
